<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. I damlai hun chawmcha sung hin,
 I pau na sem hitiu ie;
 Hun a muolliem zawh ma hin,
 Lal na sem hitiu ie.

[V2]
 Aw, a kul, Lal na sem hitiu,
 I thagau damna ahi;
 Lal na sem hitiu;
 A kul ie ! A kul ie ! ti'n gen kimvel un.

[V3]
 2. I Lal Isu Krista lo chu,
 Pathien dang a um puoh ie;
 Lei leh van vaihawmpa chu,
 Nasep in pakcha'i tiu.

[V4]
 3. Lei lopina ngaina haw vang,
 Gitloh leh pukna ahii;
 Lungsietna leh kingaihniem.
 Pielgal lampi ahi.

[V5]
 4. Vana ka pa phuhloh haw chu,
 Bawh dawk vek ding tih ahi;
 Thaklah ding aum puoh ie,
 Lal na sem hitiu ie.</lyrics>
<title>Lal Nasep A Kul Hi</title>
<hymn_number>328</hymn_number>
<author>Pautinkhup</author>
</song>